title: Howard Stern-The Sour Shoes Holiday Spectacular
description:
Howard Stern-The Sour Shoes Holiday Spectacular  (32:18)

Join Jon Leiberman & beloved Wack Pack member
Sour Shoes for a classic holiday variety show 
that will thrill & delight audiences of all ages!


* "The Noine Days Of Christmas" with GARY DELL'ABATE.
* "White Christmas" with WAYNE BRADY.
* "Santa Clause Is Coming To Town".
* Stern Family Christmas 1964. (skit)
* Sours Parents.
* A Few Wack Packer's Visit.
* Santa Clause Visits.(aka SAL)
* Steve Langford Returns.
* "Do They Know It's Christmas" All-Star Cast
